 a\ngiant impact, implying that volatile loss did not occur contemporaneously with\nimpact but following cooling and accretion of the Moon.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Dec 2018 10:35:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-27"}
