l-known algorithms on twelve benchmark data sets. Our\nexperimental analysis manifests the superiority of our proposed method over\nstate-of-art algorithms for multi-label learning.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Dec 2018 12:58:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-27"}
